Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1

Thanks for picking this up.  There seems to be a problem with the release notes (probably not your fault).  If you look at the generated html for Queens:
http://logs.openstack.org/77/654277/2/check/build-openstack-releasenotes/fd833e8/html/queens.html

The 'draft Policy Refactor spec' link is to the old location.  Same thing if you scroll down to the metadefs changes (16.0.0 > Upgrade Notes).

I didn't check any others.  I also didn't try to generate the pages locally to see if the correct links show up.  I didn't see anything on the mailing list, either.

If the HTML pages generate correctly for you locally, it may be a problem with the zuul job configuration, so if that's the case, you can ask for help in #openstack-infra.  If the links aren't correct locally, I guess the best place to ask someone is either #openstack-doc or #openstack-dev
